  "remarks": "One of the founders of Gunvor, one of the world’s largest independent commodity trading companies involved in the oil and energy markets.  Engaged in activities in the energy sector that have been directly linked to Putin, who has investments in Gunvor and might have access to Gunvor funds.  Owner and manager of the Volga Group, one of the largest investment groups in Russia; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (relisted on 16 Jun. 2017 and 10 June 2023)",
